div.div:
runSim()
- Load settings json into settings dict
- Passes along settings dict and log level to SimulationRunner
RunSimulation()
- Creates output directory
- Parses all item jsons in the "Items" directory
- Creates AgentSeed objects for each spawn type specified in settings
- Creates a SimulationManager seed
- Instantiates Connection Network
- Spawns parallel agent simulation sub-processes and passes each process a subset of AgentSeeds
- Spawns a simManager sub-process
